i><li class="EbwS_i o-iW "><a href="https://www.bikewale.com/" class="o-f o-aE o-iD" title="BikeWale" rel="noopener" target="_blank">BikeWale</a></li><li class="EbwS_i o-iW "><a href="https://www.cartrade.com/" class="o-f o-aE o-iD" title="CarTrade" rel="noopener" target="_blank">CarTrade</a></li><li class="EbwS_i o-iW "><a href="https://www.mobilityoutlook.com/" class="o-f o-aE o-iD" title="Mobility Outlook" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Mobility Outlook</a></li><li class="EbwS_i o-iW "><a href="https://www.olx.in/" class="o-f o-aE o-iD" title="OLX" rel="noopener" target="_blank">OLX</a></li><li class="EbwS_i o-iW "><div class="o-f o-aE o-iD">abSure</div></li></ul></div></div><div class="o-gr o-fT o-hA Q11zJB o-df o-dL o-lX o-mi o-aL o-rl ULdh6n"><div class="o-h o-aM o-bS o-co o-j0 o-jf"><p class=" yV2rf2">©<!-- -->CarTrade Tech.</p><div class=""><a href="/visitor-agreement/" title="Visitor Agreement" class="YaiIng">Visitor Agreement</a> &amp; <a href="/privacy-policy/" title="Privacy Policy" class="YaiIng">Privacy Policy</a></div></div></div></footer></div></div>



<script>
	window.__INITIAL_STATE__ = {"editorialDetails":{"isLocationPopupActive":false,"pageList":[{"pageId":46585,"pageName":"Page 1","content":"\u003cp\u003e- \u003ca href=\u0027https://www.carwale.com/marutisuzuki-cars/dzire-facelift/\u0027\u003eMaruti Suzuki Dzire facelift\u003c/a\u003e is offered only with a 1.2-litre DualJet VVT petrol engine\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e- The pre-facelift model was available with a 1.3-litre, four cylinder diesel engine\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\u0027https://www.carwale.com/marutisuzuki-cars/\u0027\u003eMaruti Suzuki\u003c/a\u003e recently launched the 2020 \u003ca href=\u0027https://www.carwale.com/marutisuzuki-cars/dzire-facelift/\u0027\u003eDzire facelift\u003c/a\u003e in India, details of which are available \u003ca href=\u0027https://www.carwale.com/news/2020-maruti-suzuki-dzire-facelift-launched-in-india-at-rs-589-lakh/\u0027\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e. The model in question is offered with a 1.2-litre DualJet VVT petrol engine. The company did not announce any details regarding the diesel engine, hinting that it has been discontinued.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca href=\u0027https://www.carwale.com/marutisuzuki-cars/dzire/\u0027\u003eMaruti Suzuki Dzire\u003c/a\u003e (pre-facelift) was available with a 1.3-litre, four cylinder diesel engine that produced 74bhp and 190Nm of torque. This motor was paired to a five-speed manual transmission and an AMT unit. The Maruti \u003ca href=\u0027https://www.carwale.com/marutisuzuki-cars/dzire/\u0027\u003eDzire\u003c/a\u003e diesel variant was offered in seven trims including LDi, VDi, VDi AGS, ZDi, ZDi AGS, ZDi Plus and ZDi Plus AGS.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAs the diesel engine has been discontinued, the Maruti Dzire is offered only with a 1.2-litre Dualjet petrol engine that produces 89bhp and 113Nm. Transmission options include a five-speed manual transmission and an AMT unit.\u003c/p\u003e","publishedTime":"08:35 PM","sectionScore":0.0,"pageType":"","updationDate":"03/20/2020 20:35:34"}],"relatedArticles":[],"vernacularArticleVersions":[],"articleUrl":"/news/maruti-suzuki-dzire-diesel-variants-discontinued/","imagePath":"https://imgd.aeplcdn.com/664x374/n/cw/ec/46045/marutisuzuki-dzire-exterior0.jpeg?wm=1\u0026q=80","basicId":46045,"categoryId":1,"authorMaskingName":"aditya-nadkarni","authorName":"Aditya Nadkarni","authorImageUrl":"https://imgd.aeplcdn.com/104x104/n/xpmdusa_1482436.jpg","isAuthorActive":true,"mainImgCaption":"","publishedDate":"March 21, 2020, 12:26 PM","socialMediaDetails":{"faceBookShareUrl":"http://m.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://carwale.com/news/maruti-suzuki-dzire-diesel-variants-discontinued/?utm_source=share\u0026t=Maruti Suzuki Dzire diesel variants discontinued","gmailShareUrl":"mailto:noreply@carwale.com?subject=Maruti Suzuki Dzire diesel variants discontinued\u0026body=I was reading https://www.carwale.com/news/maruti-suzuki-dzire-diesel-variants-discontinued/?utm_source=share on CarWale site and thought to share with you.","whatsShareUrl":"whatsapp://send?text=https://www.carwale.com/news/maruti-suzuki-dzire-diesel-variants-discontinued/?utm_source=share","twitterShareUrl":"https://twitter.com/share?url=https://www.carwale.com/news/maruti-suzuki-dzire-diesel-variants-discontinued/?utm_source=share\u0026t=Maruti Suzuki Dzire diesel variants discontinued","dataLabel":"https://www.carwale.com/news/maruti-suzuki-dzire-diesel-variants-discontinued/"},"tagsList":["Maruti Suzuki","DZire","Maruti Suzuki Dzire"],"title":"Maruti Suzuki Dzire diesel variants discontinued","vehicleTagsList":[{"makeBase":{"makeId":10,"makeName":"Maruti Suzuki","maskingName":"maruti-suzuki"},"modelBase":{"modelId":1327,"modelName":"Dzire [2020-2024]","maskingName":"dzire-2020-2024","status":"3","imagePath":"https://imgd.aeplcdn.com/664x374/n/cw/ec/45691/dzire-exterior-right-front-three-quarter-3.jpeg?isig=0\u0026q=80","formattedPrice":"Rs. 6.50 Lakh","priceLabel":"Avg. Ex-Showroom price","priceSuffix":"onwards"},"versionBase":{"id":-1,"name":""}}],"makeName":"Maruti Suzuki","modelName":"Dzire [2020-2024]","modelMaskingName":"dzire-2020-2024","modelStatus":3,"makeMaskingName":"maruti-suzuki","imagesCount":20,"is360Available":false,"articleSchema":"{\u0022@context\u0022:\u0022http://schema.org\u0022,\u0022@type\u0022:\u0022NewsArticle\u0022,\u0022inLanguage\u0022:\u0022English\u0022,\u0022headline\u0022:\u0022Maruti Suzuki Dzire diesel variants discontinued\u0022,\u0022description\u0022:\u0022The Maruti Suzuki Dzire facelift is offered only with a 1.2-litre DualJet VVT petrol engine.\u0022,\u0022articleBody\u0022:\u0022 - Maruti Suzuki Dzire facelift is offered only with a 1.2-litre DualJet VVT petrol engine- The pre-facelift model was available with a 1.3-litre, four cylinder diesel engineMaruti Suzuki recently launched the 2020 Dzire facelift in India, details of which are available here. The model in question is offered with a 1.2-litre DualJet VVT petrol engine. The company did not announce any details regarding the diesel engine, hinting that it has been discontinued.The Maruti Suzuki Dzire (pre-facelift) was available with a 1.3-litre, four cylinder diesel engine that produced 74bhp and 190Nm of torque. This motor was paired to a five-speed manual transmission and an AMT unit. The Maruti Dzire diesel variant was offered in seven trims including LDi, VDi, VDi AGS, ZDi, ZDi AGS, ZDi Plus and ZDi Plus AGS.As the diesel engine has been discontinued, the Maruti Dzire is offered only with a 1.2-litre Dualjet petrol engine that produces 89bhp and 113Nm. Transmission options include a five-speed manual transmission and an AMT unit.\u0022,\u0022mainEntityOfPage\u0022:{\u0022@type\u0022:\u0022WebPage\u0022,\u0022@id\u0022:\u0022https://www.carwale.com/news/maruti-suzuki-dzire-diesel-variants-discontinued/\u0022},\u0022datePublished\u0022:\u00222020-03-21T12:26:57+05:30\u0022,\u0022dateCreated\u0022:\u00222020-03-20T20:33:57+05:30\u0022,\u0022dateModified\u0022:\u00222020-03-20T20:33:57+05:30\u